    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-16">
      <p class="lead text-xl text-gray-600">
        Iceland's diverse landscapes offer photographers an otherworldly playground of natural wonders.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Prime Photo Locations</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
      {photoSpots.map(spot => (
        <PhotoSpot {...spot} />
      ))}
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Photography Tips</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      {photographyTips.map(tip => (
        <PhotoTip {...tip} />
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>Essential Information</h2>
      <h3>Best Seasons</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Summer for midnight sun (June-August)</li>
        <li>Winter for Northern Lights (September-March)</li>
        <li>Shoulder seasons for balanced conditions</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Equipment Recommendations</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Weather-sealed camera body</li>
        <li>Wide-angle lens (14-35mm)</li>
        <li>Neutral density filters</li>
        <li>Sturdy tripod</li>
        <li>Lens cleaning supplies</li>
      </ul>

      <blockquote>
        <p>"Iceland's landscapes demand patience and resilience, but reward photographers with truly unique imagery."</p>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>